title: I Got Juana Back a Journey of Inspiration
description: Motivational speaker turned author Juana Wooldridge brings hope, inspiration, drive and determination She challenges her audience, daring them to be more than they ever expected as she shares her story. A single mother with the drive to win against all odds. She encourages, cajoles, and sometimes scolds as she takes the audience on a journey to self-awareness.
author: Juana Woolridge
